{"tid":2510902,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"有貓B係寵物展入面比狗咬死 (6)","createTime":"2021-04-30T13:07:25.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-30T13:26:00.000Z","uid":240902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"68ff94d4622daa2698c70d0dc761e323bd32b628","tid":2510902,"uid":240902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T13:07:25.000Z","msg":"<strong><em><span class=\"x-large\">大家依家可以做嘅野：</span></em></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\">1.有任何當日影咗相/有相關證據/在場目擊者</span> 盡快聯絡貓主FB: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/btg.gloria\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fbtg.gloria&d=SQXEpmicj55cx%2FeODTqnTx3udkpk2VnOHMKOPHAv%2FIQ%3D&h=82bb593a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/btg.gloria</a><br />\n人證好重要！<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\">2.罷買pet pet express+FB一星評分追擊</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/petpetexpress/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fpetpetexpress%2F&d=SQXEpmicj55cx%2FeODTqnTx3udkpk2VnOHMKOPHAv%2FIQ%3D&h=f752feb1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/petpetexpress/</a><br />\n直到佢解釋點解佢唔喺現場<br />\n但係時候就開live暗示/指責可能係隻貓挑釁隻狗呢（有圖證明狗主係佢顧客 有幫佢宣傳 ig賣廣告）但係咁樣就可以盲撐狗主？<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\">3.狗主以後賣親任何廣告宣傳全部罷買</span> 唔好再比佢哋消費隻狗ig打卡拎去賣廣告 但係又唔教好<br />\n等人知道佢哋幾冷血 社會性死亡<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\">4.去寵物展主辦方FB</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/petshowhk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fpetshowhk%2F&d=SQXEpmicj55cx%2FeODTqnTx3udkpk2VnOHMKOPHAv%2FIQ%3D&h=c14138b5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/petshowhk/</a><br />\n用輿論壓力等佢盡快交cctv/協助一切調查事宜 同埋點樣避免下次意外發生<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><strong><em>有關資料：</em></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://youtu.be/S8a39LcIheA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FS8a39LcIheA&d=SQXEpmicj55cx%2FeODTqnTx3udkpk2VnOHMKOPHAv%2FIQ%3D&h=cabde3a2\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/S8a39LcIheA</a><br />\n\t<br />\npetpetexpress老闆facebook live backup<br />\n老闆因為身有屎 已經del左條片<br />\n<br />\n有貓B係寵物展入面比狗咬死 (3)狗主死全家<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/aNgmBJV\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/aNgmBJV</a><br />\n#32 回覆 - 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\npetpetexpress 價錢比較<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmWnnMyrtmnP1LRSZaBSaFFfX4F3z3KHYLfZ5m6KfSpP2Q?filename=xotOQ4T.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxotOQ4T.png&h=4e0dc8e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n事主facebook post<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmW5kFyu9JNJHtN9r9etpjvQMoPXdcz5wDSgaWYB734asK?filename=BE92VwA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBE92VwA.jpg&h=69b2c114&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n貓b<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qmdhse5njMyEquBh5GSWubayKPea86Qd5kifPgcJgfoy6b?filename=mywT2bC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmywT2bC.jpg&h=72ccc532&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n咬死貓b嘅柴犬<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmZzXhWf8AqVeeT1z6eTuZ2nywKj1TychGabxxNG7S1qnd?filename=H5jB8ga.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH5jB8ga.png&h=53b3a1fe&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmSrSdzQ1caHxfXUNrzHkggUp5MEYNXx4m76CWGzTD692M?filename=5fXzUWb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5fXzUWb.jpg&h=29e77b72&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n其他受害者<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qmc8dRsk5MrSMY4gZDXMaJb41iboGGQByGgJY9tWHfN9Mq?filename=GV0E522.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGV0E522.jpg&h=226677c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n狗主「道歉」facebook post<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmNMm145rQcfR9kZFVj7PicG67B7nANARmvdzEcjDsdqAd?filename=rfWkQu4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thu